# Testing gates

## Always run

```bash
npm run build -w @all-according-to-plan/shared -w @all-according-to-plan/game-engine
```

Web touched: `cd apps/web && npm run build && npm run lint`

## Engine logic change

Until Vitest exists: **Gate D** manual checklist in agent report (min 3 repro steps, cite state fields).

When Vitest exists: `npm test -w @all-according-to-plan/game-engine` — **required**, no waiver.

## cards.json only

Build workspaces that depend on shared; manual UI spot-check steps.

## Prohibited claims

- "Tests pass" without command output
- "Comprehensive coverage" for unrelated UI diff

## Test design

- Fixed `gameSeed` from `createInitialState`
- Assert numeric state fields, not snapshots of entire UI
